@startuml SME_Ops_Sequence_Customer
title UC12 — Create or update customer — §2.3.7

actor Cashier
participant "Customers UI" as Web
participant "CustomersController" as API
participant "CustomersService" as Svc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Cashier -> Web : save customer form
Web -> API : POST or PATCH /customers
API -> Svc : create/update(dto, orgId)
Svc -> DB : insert or update Customer
DB --> Svc : customer
Svc --> API : customer DTO
API --> Web : 200/201
Web --> Cashier : refresh list

@enduml
